image.altText: Lisa Wilkinson smiling enters Federal Court in Sydney before Bruce Lehrmann defamation judgment, media around

image.altText: Generic AFP Badge

image.altText: A sign on the front of a building saying 'Genius Childcare', photographed through bars.

But the scale of what the archaeological team found was staggering — and the job of putting names to the many bones was "like a giant puzzle".
